---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us - Abbotsford's Best" description="Learn about Abbotsford's Best and our mission to connect the community with the best local businesses">
  <Header />

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-primary-700 text-white py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">About Abbotsford's Best</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-primary-100">
        Connecting our community with the finest local businesses since day one
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="prose prose-lg mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Our Mission</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          At Abbotsford's Best, we're committed to showcasing the city's finest businesses and helping local entrepreneurs grow with useful information. Our mission is simple: to connect you with the best services, vendors, and professionals Abbotsford has to offer.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 mt-12">What Makes Us Different</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          We don't do paid placements. Our featured businesses earn their spots through community recommendations, quality service, and genuine customer satisfaction. We believe in authentic endorsements from real Abbotsford residents who've experienced these businesses firsthand.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 mt-12">Community-Driven Approach</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Our recommendations come directly from Facebook groups and community discussions where real residents share their experiences. This grassroots approach ensures you're getting honest, trustworthy referrals from your neighbors.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 mt-12">Supporting Local Business</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Today's entrepreneurial landscape is filled with opportunities and challenges. We're here to help local businesses build their digital presence and connect with customers who value quality service and community engagement.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>